---
title: Speedy Chicken Chili with Ciabatta Croutons
description: This delicious chicken chili comes together in no time! We've packed it with warming spices, hearty beans and plenty of fresh veggies to satisfy the whole family on a cold winter's night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chili-au-poulet-36ff3f16.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/speedy-chicken-chili-6304939fff7b8862e100db0f-a05ab9a4.pdf
